Comment 1: sharp merge point coinciding with cars exiting/entering shopping centre drive ways. This made worse when congestion during busy times and car speeds perhaps too high for the conditions. The shopping centre drive ways (entry and exits) and are also not clearly marked nor has signage, so confusing as to where/when cars should stop/turn in to or out of the area.
